name: Faith Lutheran Church
review_text: I have never been to this church for a service or anything but I see the pastor and Bob and Vance use their time delivering goods for the apartments across the street, they do it with great care and compassion, every week they walk around the complex passing out donated food and goodies. This is what love and brotherhood is all about as actions speak louder than words... Way to go guys and may your church and people be blessed as you do great things for this community!! üíí ü§óüôèüèª
